
# Definir variable token vacía
@token =

### Registro de usuario
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "name": "User Uno",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Guardar token automáticamente
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### Obtener perfil (requiere token)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear libro (requiere token de librarian/admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "isbn": "9781234567890",
  "title": "Libro de Prueba",
  "author": "Autor Prueba",
  "genre": "Ficción",
  "publishedYear": 2024,
  "copies": 5
}

### Listar libros
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books

### Solicitar préstamo (requiere token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "bookId": 1
}

### Devolver libro (requiere token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Crear reseña (requiere token)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Excelente libro!"
}

### Listar reseñas de un libro
GET http://localhost:3000/api/books/1/reviews

### Eliminar reseña (requiere token)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
